The function can utilize dynamic programming to track whether each prefix of the string can be segmented into words from the given list.

```python
def word_break(s, words):
    dp = [False] * (len(s) + 1)
    dp[0] = True
    for i in range(1, len(s) + 1):
        for j in range(i):
            if dp[j] and s[j:i] in words:
                dp[i] = True
                break
    return dp[-1]
```
